high_descs: Take a left, head to the black table in the corner
Take the butter knife from the table
Turn around, head to the round black table in the corner
Put the knife in the black mug on the table
Take the black mug from the table
Turn around, head back to the black table in the corner
put the black mug on the black table
anns.task_desc: Put the knife in the black mug, put the mug on the square black table

high_descs: Turn left, walk across the room, then turn right to face the black table.
Pick up the silver knife on the black table.
Turn around and walk across the room the face the kitchen table.
Place the knife in the vase on the left.
Pick up the vase with a knife in it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the black table.
Place the vase with a knife in it on the black table.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in a vase as well as move it to a black end table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then turn right.
Pick up the butter knife you see on the small black table's front edge.
Turn around and walk to the black table.
Put the knife in the cup that's closer to the egg.
Pick up the cup that has a knife in it.
Turn around and walk to the small black table again.
Put the cup to the left of the black plate.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: turn left, walk to the wall, turn right to face the end table
pick up the butter knife on the end table
turn around and walk to the round table
put the knife in a cup
pick up the cup on the round table
Turn around and walk back to the end table
set the cup on the end table
anns.task_desc: put the knife in a cup on the end table

high_descs: Turn left and face the small black table next to the wall to the right.
Pick up the butter knife near the edge of the table.
Turn around and walk to the round black table.
Place the butter knife in the black cup closest to the brown weight.
Pick up the black cup with the butter knife inside of it.
Turn around and walk to the small black table.
Place the cup with the butter knife to the left of the square plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the cup with the butter knife in it next to a square plate on the square table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the door, then turn right to face the small black table.
Pickup the butter knife from the table.
Turn around and walk towards the black circle table.
Place the knife inside the cup on the left.
Pick up the cup.
Turn around and walk towards the small black table.
Place the cup to the left of the black plate.
anns.task_desc: Place the knife inside the cup.
